  "name": "Morrison COU2 — VAD hemolysis credibility assessment (W-EP-02 adversarial sample)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU2 evaluates whether the computational model can predict absolute hemolysis levels for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification is performed across five flow-speed combinations. This package is a synthetic adversarial sample targeting W-EP-02: one ValidationResult (the most narratively detailed) carries no prov:wasGeneratedBy link to a generation Activity, breaking structured provenance while appearing complete to a casual reviewer.",
