      "rationale": "The proprietary VAD operates at different flow rates (4–6 L/min) and rotational speeds (2800–3800 RPM) than the FDA benchmark operating points used for validation. No formal equivalency mapping or extrapolation uncertainty was computed. Input parameter equivalency is entirely unassessed. Achieved level 1 against required level 4."
    }
